teemed athlete, Imane Khelif, with baseless propaganda from certain foreign media outlets,\\\" it said in a statement.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.450820451513478e-19, \"text\": \"COA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Such attacks on her personality and dignity are deeply unfair, especially as she prepares for the pinnacle of her career at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The COA has taken all necessary measures to protect our champion.\\\"\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1236, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.450820451513478e-19, \"text\": \"COA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Italy's Family Minister Eugenia Roccella and Sports Minister Andrea Abodi voiced rconcern about the eligibility rules on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9909747676985718, \"rank\": 0.008510670336711048, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eugenia\", \"score\": 0.9997276834349269, \"rank\": 0.0002671005972884608, \"text\": \"Eugenia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eugenia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eugenia\"}, {\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.S.D._Roccella\", \"score\": 0.9999963492044366, \"rank\": 3.573109583172625e-06, \"text\": \"Roccella\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.S.D._Roccella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.S.D._Roccella\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is surprising that there are no certain, strict, uniform criteria at the international level,\\\" Roccella said.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.S.D._Roccella\", \"score\": 0.9999963492044366, \"rank\": 3.573109583172625e-06, \"text\": \"Roccella\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.S.D._Roccella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.S.D._Roccella\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added that it was strange \\\"that there can be a suspicion, and far more than a suspicion, of an unfair and potentially dangerous contest for one of the contenders at the Olympics, an event that symbolizes sporting fairness\\\".\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Abodi questioned a lack of alignment in \\\"parameters of minimum hormonal values.\\\"\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the event that represents the highest values of sport, the safety of female and male athletes must be guaranteed, as well as respect for fair competition,\\\" Abodi added.\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That is not how it will be tomorrow for Angela Carini.\\\"\", \"from\"